The paper deals with the broadcast problem in wireless networks, which is a topic related to networked systems and communication (cs.NI). The use of a labelling scheme suggests a focus on data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). The proposed algorithms and strategies also involve system design and control (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG).
